00:13:02,690 --> 00:13:04,770
and Katie's new kidney is functioning well.

320
00:13:04,770 --> 00:13:05,800
Thank God.

321
00:13:05,800 --> 00:13:09,410
Will her ruptured vein have any effect on our separation surgery?

322
00:13:09,500 --> 00:13:10,610
It better not.

323
00:13:10,610 --> 00:13:11,270
Katie, I love you,

